fields.description:
{panel:bgColor=#e7f4fa}
  *NOTE:* This bug report is for *Confluence Cloud*. Using *Confluence Server*? [See the corresponding bug report|http://jira.atlassian.com/browse/CONFSERVER-49947].
  {panel}

It's very edge case that if I add an yearly event to February 29th (e.g 20/Feb/2016) in a leap year, I expect the event will appear on 29/Feb/2020, but it is displayed in 28/Feb/2020.

{panel:bgColor=#e7f4fa}
  *NOTE:* This bug report is for *Confluence Cloud*. Using *Confluence Server*? [See the corresponding bug report|http://jira.atlassian.com/browse/CONFSERVER-49946].
  {panel}

